# Google Drive BYOC backup (PRD Section 16) — optional.
# Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application) in Google Cloud Console
# with the Drive API enabled. Client IDs are not secret and are safe to
# ship in client-side code — no client secret is used or needed here.
# Leave unset to ship without cloud backup; local .codex export/import
# always works with no configuration.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
